- [x] Heading groups are created from well-chained heading blocks

<div column-grid font-size:=75%>

```md
# Heading 1
## Subheading

---
## Heading 2
### Subheading
#### Subsubheading

---
# Heading 1
### Heading 3

---
# Heading 1

## Heading 2
```

